{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b6564987-bd1a-4119-b59b-6cb478f0e9ae","content":"No files found in the workspace — I'll explain the conversion directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` to enable compiled bindings:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n        <Slider Value=\"{Binding FontSize}\" Minimum=\"8\" Maximum=\"32\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key changes:**\n1. Add `xmlns:vm` pointing to your ViewModel namespace.\n2. Add `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` on the `ContentPage`.\n3. All `{Binding}` expressions are now validated at compile time.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nCompiled bindings already emit **build errors** for typos or type mismatches (e.g., `{Binding Themee}` won't compile).\n\nTo **enforce** this project-wide and block any uncompiled bindings from slipping through, add to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n    <!-- Treat warnings from uncompiled bindings as errors -->\n    <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n## Tips\n\n- If a child element binds to a **different type** (e.g., an item template), set `x:DataType` locally on that element.\n- To **opt out** for a specific binding (e.g., `RelativeSource`), use `x:DataType=\"x:Null\"` on that element.\n- The ViewModel must be a **concrete type** (not `object` or `BindableObject`) for the compiler to resolve properties.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"7fcea363-5daa-4937-9afb-608d6a6ac3b5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There are no files in the current directory. The user is asking a general question about how to convert a .NET MAUI page to use compiled bindings. Let me provide them with a clear, concise answer.","outputTokens":602,"requestId":"1437:2EDED2:702BB6D:7861B8A:6A03CC00"},"id":"d6b36962-c994-44e4-a2f0-e5335aa74341","timestamp":"2026-05-13T00:55:41.189Z","parentId":"7b7dd8d8-ff7f-4e1b-8f8f-2d7b48b29187"}
